org.efaps.admin.datamodel.ui

Class LinkWithRangesUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.ui.AbstractUI
      • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.ui.LinkWithRangesUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IUIProvider, UIInterface

    public class LinkWithRangesUI
extends AbstractUI
    This Class is the representation of LinkWithRanges for the user interface.
    Depending on the access mode (e.g. edit) the Value of a Field is presented in an editable or non editable mode.
